						<summary>

						<p>Vijayanagara, Kṛishṇarāya-Mahārāya, Śaka 1447, Pārthiva, Dakshiṇāyana, Tulā, sudi 5, Friday, Mṛigaśīsha = A.D. 1525, October 6, Friday.</p>						

						<p>A major part in the middle is worn out. This seems to record a gift of land by the <hi rend="italic">nāṭṭavar</hi> of Valla-nāḍu to the temple for the health of some <hi rend="italic">nāyakkar</hi> (most probably Vīranarasiṅga-rāya-nāyakkar).</p>						

						<p>[Published in <hi rend="italic">IPS</hi>, No. 738.]</p>						

